title: Malaysia Gross National Income
description: Gross National Product in Malaysia increased to 374.70 MYR Billion in the third quarter of 2022 from 358.70 MYR Billion in the second quarter of 2022. Gross National Product in Malaysia averaged 245.28 MYR Billion from 2005 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 374.70 MYR Billion in the third quarter of 2022 and a record low of 127.10 MYR Billion in the first quarter of 2005. This page provides - Malaysia Gross National Income - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Statistics, Malaysia
